text:
Mmm, it's prefect!
I think it looks great!

Wait a moment～... I've got some accessories that will go well...
Oh────?

Oh my... this is a pretty old outfit......
Looks like it got lost in here.

Yes... I think it must be several years old...
Given how wrinkled it's become.
So they still keep even old costumes around, huh.

Oh well... Hard to say whose it might be...
since a lot of people come and go in this industry...
I better keep this safe for now......

Um, Hey ────...
How about those accessories......?

Oh my, I'm so sorry.
Just a moment, okay～
